    <item>
      <title>选举争议导致莫桑比克全国暴力事件蔓延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/mozambique-death-and-looting-rock-nation-in-wake-of-disputed-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在去年 10 月有争议的选举中，执政党获得确认胜选后，莫桑比克全国各地的暴力事件于周二愈演愈烈，暴徒抢劫并焚烧了这个天然气资源丰富的东南部非洲国家的警察局，造成至少 21 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/mozambique-death-and-looting-rock-nation-in-wake-of-disputed-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 06:52:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯在圣诞节袭击乌克兰能源网络</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/ukraine-limits-power-supplies-amid-russian-attack-at-christmas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯对乌克兰能源基础设施发动大规模导弹袭击，导致该国电网运营商在圣诞节当天限制电力供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/ukraine-limits-power-supplies-amid-russian-attack-at-christmas</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 06:15:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹永康再次逃避戒严令问询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/south-korea-s-yoon-skips-questioning-again-over-martial-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈再次拒绝接受调查人员有关其戒严令的质询，这位陷入困境的领导人试图在弹劾审判中首先为自己辩护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/south-korea-s-yoon-skips-questioning-again-over-martial-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 03:14:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多忙于工作，育空地区就熊肉零食问题游说小唐纳德</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/with-trudeau-busy-yukon-lobbies-don-jr-over-bear-meat-snacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管当选总统唐纳德·特朗普在不到一个月的时间内上任后，加拿大就面临与美国的大规模贸易战，但贾斯汀·特鲁多却因领导危机而分心，这可能会让他失去总理职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/with-trudeau-busy-yukon-lobbies-don-jr-over-bear-meat-snacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 22:10:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其将最低工资提高 30%，降息可能性增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/turkey-raises-minimum-wage-30-for-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其将于2025年将最低工资标准提高30％，这让那些寻求采取具体措施撤回民粹主义政策并致力于抑制全球最高通胀率之一的投资者松了一口气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/turkey-raises-minimum-wage-30-for-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 17:51:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
